16,-0.00184012,0.02143197,0.04423549,0.00140145,0.05424386,0.00574223,0.03041427,-0.02947786,0.02373161,0.07298018,0.00541221,0.01482277,-0.04283525,0.01534163,0.01315534,-0.00277201,-0.01452016,-0.08522495,-0.01939588,-0.01769191,-0.00447388,0.00976040,-0.02863320,-0.04128846,-0.04579159,0.02504246,0.02154309,0.04770745,-0.08654817,0.02940670,-0.01339770,0.03129149,-0.00039988,-0.01434012,0.04053722,-0.06111783,0.08014029,0.00023229,0.02562093,0.07477061,0.05200845,-0.02468022]',E'Dependency Injection\n\nYou may type-hint any dependencies required by your route in your route''s callback signature. The declared dependencies will automatically be resolved and injected into the callback by the Laravel [service container](/docs/{{version}}/container). For example, you may type-hint the `Illuminate\\Http\\Request` class to have the current HTTP request automatically injected into your route callback:\n\n```php\nuse Illuminate\\Http\\Request;\n\nRoute::get(''/users'', function (Request $request) {\n    // ...\n});\n```\n\n<a name="csrf-protection"></a>','{"source": "laravel", "version": "12", "language": "php", "title": "Routing", "section_title": "routing", "url": "https://github.com/laravel/docs/blob/12.x/routing.md", "topics": "laravel,php,routing", "categories": "web,php,fullstack,orm"}');
