.19385707,0.00361878,-0.00406559,-0.03938043,0.01543226,-0.02461020,0.01143261,0.05679330,0.04586287,0.02014146,0.15674102,0.02682185,-0.03772970,0.00546699,-0.02267534,0.05776468,-0.03136474,-0.06606437,-0.06028350,0.01965734,-0.05468380,0.03714261,0.01435279,0.02046821,-0.07027230,0.05618770,-0.03462849,0.01172048,0.00730149,-0.00433807,-0.00994440,-0.04688470,0.03381267,0.01037680,0.06096237,-0.00666512,0.00827841,0.08001019,-0.01428719,0.05261207,0.04591769,0.03794596,-0.00390271]',E'Pending Attributes\n\nclass Post extends Model\n{\n    /**\n     * Scope the query to only include drafts.\n     */\n    #[Scope]\n    protected function draft(Builder $query): void\n    {\n        $query->withAttributes([\n            ''hidden'' => true,\n        ]);\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThe `withAttributes` method will add `where` conditions to the query using the given attributes, and it will also add the given attributes to any models created via the scope:\n\n```php\n$draft = Post::draft()->create([''title'' => ''In Progress'']);','{"source": "laravel", "version": "12", "language": "php", "title": "Eloquent: Getting Started", "section_title": "eloquent", "url": "https://github.com/laravel/docs/blob/12.x/eloquent.md", "topics": "laravel,php,eloquent", "categories": "web,php,fullstack,orm"}');
